@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_peoizp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.81) + wp.abs(v2 + 0.48)) - ((v2 + 0.42 / v1 + 0.24) - (tmp + 0.88 - v1 + 0.29)))
    v0 = 0.19
    v1 = v1
    v1 = v0
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.abs((v0 + 0.39 + v0 + 0.43)))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.cos((v1 + 0.08 - tmp + 0.12)))
    v0 = (tmp / (wp.exp(v2 + 0.35) / (v1 + 0.81 - tmp + 0.25)))
    data[tid] = v0
